{"tid":1043637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬤嚇傻！登上冰山王座拍照 結果越漂越遠","createTime":"2019-03-02T12:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T12:50:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25ff4e5c93b9e22ffc3b60d20da3abe7bf285442","tid":1043637,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"阿嬤嚇傻！登上冰山王座拍照 結果越漂越遠... <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpsPcYTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpsPcYTa.jpg&h=fdb37aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國德州阿嬤斯特朗（Judith Streng）到冰島旅行時，坐上岸邊的「冰山王座」。（圖擷自@Xiushook推特）<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-02 10:35<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國德州77歲阿嬤斯特朗（Judith Streng），近日和兒子羅勃（Rob）來到冰島旅行，看到海岸邊的小冰山碎解成寶座的模樣，高高興興地跑上去拍照，彷彿成了冰山女王，孰料一陣海浪打來，讓阿嬤漸漸越漂越遠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php34cJjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php34cJjp.jpg&h=f111ac62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孰料冰山王座最後卻越漂越遠，幸好有其他遊客出手相救，讓阿嬤回到岸邊。（圖擷自@Xiushook推特）<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，斯特朗透露，自己一直很想要成為女王，而且在她之前已經有好幾個人上去擺姿勢拍照了，孰料她走上小冰山後開始有搖搖欲墜的感覺，可能是因為自己的體重太輕了，讓小冰山更容易浮起來。<br />\n<br />\n接著一股巨大的海浪襲來，斯特朗坐在冰山王座上慢慢地遠離岸邊，幸好現場一名遊客恰好是受過水上救援訓練的船長，很快地就幫助阿嬤回來。<br />\n<br />\n斯特朗的孫女事後在推特分享爸爸羅勃當時拍下的照片，讓不少網友驚呼連連，有人直說「女王失去國土了！」還有人調侃爸爸在這種危急情況下，竟然還在幫阿嬤拍照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713958&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=d648fec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713958&h=b5e5b411\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713958</a>"},{"pid":"4fc75ae6ef95adb2bfaf27c20363388afa7cedad","tid":1043637,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"直接海葬夠晒環保"},{"pid":"cccd540682568dac5777451d45570bf3acee28c9","tid":1043637,"uid":20815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wickedgoodgaming.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lich_King.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwickedgoodgaming.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FLich_King.jpg&h=9ea50a87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d1d28d38b8cd37d4eb95641ec2a4abd08994505","tid":1043637,"uid":138482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45315c6c5587a5ca6f375ef60158ff636e1954f6","tid":1043637,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"漂撚咗去搵屠龍刀"}]}